    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I consider this to be a bad idea.  If the \"return to base\" feature is not fit for purpose, then that should be changed.  Adding an entirely new hotkey that works *almost* the same adds UI complexity that runs against the goal of having a streamlined control scheme.\r\n\r\nThis also ties in to the long running argument about having the game play itself vs providing a skill ramp by requiring players to manage their own units."
