    "body": "@rob-v I would appreciate it if you could restart discussion on tickets before starting work on them.\r\n\r\nAnybody can file issues, and many tickets are based on opinion or frustration rather than planned game design.  It is stressful as a reviewer to have to fundamentally rewrite or reject a PR after the work has already been done – especially right now, with our constrained review bandwidth – so it would make life a lot easier if these tickets could be evaluated and a plan of attack determined (which may be closing the ticket) before the PR stage."
